---
description: AMTECH folder-first UI variant standard
globs: "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Read `README.md`, `AGENTS.md`, `contract.ts`, and the selected variant's local instruction files.
- During ordinary design work, edit only the selected variant directory.
- Preserve employee capability and information fidelity; do not preserve production-client appearance or layout by default.
- Use only the neutral model, bounded intent dispatcher, local files, declared dependencies, and optional reference-client slot.
- Never fetch product data, use ambient storage, or import application internals.
- Run `node ../../../../scripts/ui-variant.mjs validate <slug>` before stopping.
